{"tid":2347423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本夫妻嗌交後翌日 老公午餐便當飯盒變成咁","createTime":"2020-12-31T04:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T09:39:00.000Z","uid":36494,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c82a93c0dfa5a0f3f301f033b2a66b667f709aa8","tid":2347423,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"唔好同米飯班主嗌求係常識，不過總有人重複犯錯嘅，日本呢位人夫噚晚同老婆嗌完交，第二日發現個便當變咗左邊張圖咁嘅樣‥‥‥飯盒入面得對筷子，而個筷子盒入面就塞滿飯，不過有粒酸梅都算俾面喇。之後唔少網民分享佢哋嘅慘痛經驗，犯案者有阿媽有老婆，所以都係唔好得罪女人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameover.com.hk/news/479387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameover.com.hk%2Fnews%2F479387&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=6a576b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameover.com.hk/news/479387</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YMqqvvv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYMqqvvv.png&h=c94deef1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1B9cJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1B9cJQ.png&h=1f71b359&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYfU8hb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYfU8hb.png&h=df90c320&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhx03Qx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqhx03Qx.png&h=98c7bdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHpnxJT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHpnxJT.png&h=abd3a129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbbf471f4a269460be83e83d593bb4b54693135d","tid":2347423,"uid":66945,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"仲整比佢都算有心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18304dbf8b4d61be8a9689d32b0169015809045","tid":2347423,"uid":86124,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"最後個蛋糕係